India RBI Eases Overseas Borrowing Rules for Hotels, Hospitals

-- B y   U n n i   K r i s h n a n
-- 
2011-09-26T14:11:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/india-rbi-eases-overseas-borrowing-rules-for-hotels-hospitals.html
The  Reserve Bank  of  India  eased
overseas borrowing rules for service sector companies including
hotels, hospitals and those developing software, according to an
e-mailed statement today.  The central bank also eased similar norms for
infrastructure companies, RBI said in a separate statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
